## Requirements

- Python 3.8+
- FFmpeg (with ffprobe) installed and in PATH

### Installing FFmpeg

**Ubuntu/Debian:**
```bash
sudo apt install ffmpeg
```

**macOS:**
```bash
brew install ffmpeg
```

**Windows:**
Download from [ffmpeg.org](https://ffmpeg.org/download.html) and add to PATH.
